# SECTION 20: VERY IMPORTANT TEACHING SUMMARY
# =====================================================================
# PULL REQUEST WORKFLOW:
# feature branch -> push -> PR -> review -> update -> merge
#
# REBASE:
# used when you want your branch to sit on top of latest main
#
# SQUASH:
# used when you want many small commits to become one clean commit
#
# GITHUB PR MERGE OPTIONS:
# - Create a merge commit
# - Squash and merge
# - Rebase and merge
